Package: ldsr
Type: Package
Title: Linear Dynamical System Reconstruction
Version: 0.0.1.5
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hung", "Nguyen", email = "ntthung@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Stefano", "Galelli", email = "stefano_galelli@sutd.edu.sg", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Streamflow (and climate) reconstruction using Linear Dynamical Systems. The advantage of this method is the additional state trajectory which can reveal more information about the catchment or climate system. For details of the method please refer to Nguyen and Galelli (2018).
